title: Uber To Challenge New York Law
text:
22 Uber To Challenge New York Law 
Government Technology: On the state Capitol's 118-year-old Million Dollar Staircase, Uber Technologies Inc. and state lawmakers painted a picture of a region slipping behind in the sharing economy because New York state law does not permit transportation network companies.
